take_effect: TermPointToAmf_pwsRestartHandling__Next PWS restart or failure message to be transmitted on the NG-C interface. Does not affect ongoing PWS broadcast.

TermPointToENodeB_ipsecEpAddress__Next MO unlock for the change by operator.. Outer IP address received from X2 neighbor node overwrites manual configuration by operator, and manual configuration is ignored.

TermPointToENodeB_upIpAddress__Next MO unlock for the change by operator.. User plan address received from X2 neighbor node overwrites manual configuration by operator, and manual configuration is ignored.
TermPointToGNodeB_ipv4Address__Next MO unlock if changed by operator
TermPointToGNodeB_ipv6Address__Next MO unlock if changed by operator
GNBCUUPFunction_endcUlNrRetProhibTimer__Embedded PPF: Next Cell Unlock, Virtualized PPF: New Connection
CommonBeamforming_coverageShape__For Low-Band and Mid-Band cells, takes effect immediately. For High-Band cells, takes effect at next NRSectorCarrier unlock.
GNBDUFunction_pwsEtwsPrimaryInd__Next F1 Application Protocol (F1AP) WRITE-REPLACE WARNING REQUEST message. Does not affect ongoing PWS broadcast.
NRCellDU_advancedDlSuMimoEnabled__Immediately. For UEs configured with SRS, takes effect immediately after SRS resources are released.
NRSectorCarrier_txPowerChangeRate__In an unlocked NRSectorCarrier a change will take effect at the next change of txPowerRatio.

NRSectorCarrier_txPowerRatio__If a previous change in txPowerRatio is currently ongoing, the latest change will be started once the previous change has completed. Otherwise the current change will be started immediately.
Paging_defaultPagingCycle__After all the cells in the same gNodeB-DU have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_n__After all the cells in the same gNodeB-DU have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_nS__After all the cells in the same gNodeB-DU have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
BandCombCompression_requestMaxCCsDL__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandCombCompression_requestMaxCCsUL__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandCombCompression_requestReducedFormat__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandCombCompression_requestReducedIntNonContComb__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandCombCompression_requestSkipFallbackComb__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandCombCompression_requestedBandCombCompression__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandCombCompression_requestedFreqBandsFiltered__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandIndication_bandEUtra__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandIndication_caBandwidthClassDl__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
BandIndication_caBandwidthClassUl__At next UE Capability Enquiry including at new connection.
CarrierAggregationFunction_dlOnlySCellPriorityEnabled__At the next initial SCell selection during the ongoing connection
CarrierAggregationFunction_fddTddSCellPriority__At the next initial SCell selection during the ongoing connection
CarrierAggregationFunction_pdcchEnhancedLaForVolte__At the next initial SCell selection during the ongoing connection
CarrierAggregationFunction_waitForBlindSelSCellRepLessTtt__New connection. Also during ongoing connection, related to next SCell configuration during the connection.
CarrierAggregationFunction_requestedBandCombCompresssion__Takes effect at next UE capability refresh.
CellSleepFunction_covCellDlPrbWakeUpThresHigh__If wakeup threshold change during sleep state (Sleep Request sent), then new values dont take effect until next Sleep Request.
CellSleepFunction_covCellRrcConnWakeUpThresHigh__If wakeup threshold change during sleep state (Sleep Request sent), then new values dont take effect until next Sleep Request.
CellSleepFunction_covCellWakeUpMonitorDurTHigh__If wakeup threshold change during sleep state (Sleep Request sent), then new values dont take effect until next Sleep Request.
ENodeBFunction_ulPhyProcResTradingEnabled__After all cells in the eNodeB have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
EUtranCellFDD_caPrioThreshold__New connection or next SCell configuration.

EUtranCellRelation_sCellCandidate__Changed value will take effect in relation to the next SCell configuration during the ongoing connection. When going from state NOT_ALLOWED to ALLOWED the SCell will not be available at re-selection for ongoing connections.
EUtranCellRelation_sCellPriority__New connection or next SCell configuration.
EUtranCellTDD_caPrioThreshold__New connection or next SCell configuration.
EUtranFreqRelation_caFreqPriority__New connection or next SCell configuration.
EUtranFreqRelation_caFreqProportion__New connection or next SCell configuration.
ExternalENodeBFunction_eranLinkMaxRttDelay__Change takes effect at ERAN link setup.

ExternalENodeBFunction_eranPrioritizationDisabled__Next tunnel setup. The TermPointToENB.administrativeState attribute under ExternalENodeBFunction MO instance must be set to LOCKED and then to UNLOCKED.
Paging_defaultPagingCycle__After all cells in the RBS are locked and then unlocked. Lock/unlock cells manually, immediately after changing defaultPagingCycle.
Paging_defaultPagingCycleNbIot__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked
Paging_maxNoOfPagingRecords__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_maxNoOfPagingRecordsNb__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_nB__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_nBBr__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_pagingDiscardTimerDrx__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_pagingDiscardTimerEdrx__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_pagingDiscardTimerEdrxNb__After all the cells in the RBS have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
ReportConfigSCellA1A2_a1a2ThresholdRsrpBidir__Changed value may take effect related to the next SCell configuration during the ongoing connection.
ReportConfigSCellA1A2_hysteresisA1A2RsrpBidirectional__New connection. Also during ongoing connection, related to next SCell configuration during the connection.
Rrc_t301Nb__Next cell unlock. Lowering the value can increase drop rate.
Rrc_t311Nb__Next cell unlock. Lowering the value can increase drop rate.

TermPointToGNB_ipsecEpAddress__Next MO unlock for the change by operator.. Outer IP address received from X2 neighbor node overwrites manual configuration by operator, and manual configuration is ignored.

TermPointToGNB_upIpAddress__Next MO unlock for the change by operator.. User plan address received from X2 neighbor node overwrites manual configuration by operator, and manual configuration is ignored.
RfBranch_dlAttenuation__If cell is locked, takes effect when cell is unlocked. If cell is unlocked, takes effect immediately.
RfBranch_dlAttenuationPerFqRange__Immediately if cell is unlocked, otherwise when cell is unlocked.
RfBranch_dlTrafficDelay__If cell is locked, takes effect when cell is unlocked. If cell is unlocked, takes effect immediately.
RfBranch_dlTrafficDelayPerFqRange__Immediately if cell is unlocked, otherwise when cell is unlocked.
RfBranch_rfPortRef__At next unlock of the SectorEquipmentFunction
RfBranch_ulAttenuation__If cell is locked, takes effect when cell is unlocked. If cell is unlocked, takes effect immediately.
RfBranch_ulAttenuationPerFqRange__Immediately if cell is unlocked, otherwise when cell is unlocked.
RfBranch_ulTrafficDelay__If cell is locked, takes effect when cell is unlocked. If cell is unlocked, takes effect immediately.
RfBranch_ulTrafficDelayPerFqRange__Immediately if cell is unlocked, otherwise when cell is unlocked.

DotGroupConfig_dotGroup__Sum of branch numbers of all dot groups must not exceed 16. For example {4,4,4,8} is not allowed because 4 + 4 + 4 + 8 > 16. Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_defaultUserName__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_defaultUserPassword__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_nmsAddress__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_nmsUserName__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_nmsUserPassword__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_serialNumber__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_serialNumberValidation__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_sshKeyValidation__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_subnet__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_sudoUserName__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_sudoUserPassword__Takes effect: Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
ORadio_txArrayCarriersGain__Next unlock of parent FieldReplaceableUnit MO.
RdData_radioDotCoverage__Next cell unlock, when MO cellPortionRd is created.
RadioPowerOverbooking_featCtrlRadioPowerOverbooking__Takes effect: next eUtran cell unlock on eNodeB, or next Utran cell unlock on RNC, or next TRX unlock on BTS.
SectorEquipmentFunction_noiseFigure__Next MO unlock or restart of radio unit (IRU).
Area_ospfAreaId__All Interface MOs are reconfigured. The OSPFv2 routes from these interfaces are removed from the routing table and traffic is impacted until OSPFv2 has converged.
Interface_interfaceAddress__The Interface MO is reconfigured. The OSPFv2 routes from this interface are removed from the routing table and traffic is impacted until OSPFv2 has converged.
Ospfv2_routerId__The OSPFv2 process is restarted. All OSPFv2 routes are removed from the routing table and traffic is impacted until OSPFv2 has converged.
NodeBFunction_dualBandSectorGroup1__At next unlock of Local Cell Group.
NodeBFunction_dualBandSectorGroup2__At next unlock of Local Cell Group.
NodeBFunction_dualBandSectorGroup3__At next unlock of Local Cell Group.
NodeBFunction_dualBandSectorGroup4__At next unlock of Local Cell Group.
NodeBFunction_dualBandSectorGroup5__At next unlock of Local Cell Group.
NodeBFunction_dualBandSectorGroup6__At next unlock of Local Cell Group.
NodeBFunction_eulFachInitialRate__Next time EulFach is activated (NodeBLocalCell::featCtrlEulFach = ON).
NodeBFunction_eulFachMinAllocation__Next time EulFach is activated (NodeBLocalCell::featCtrlEulFach = ON).
NodeBLocalCell_eulNoERgchGroups__At next setup of E-DCH Resources for this cell.
NodeBLocalCell_localCellId__When local cell is idle, i.e. not set up by the RNC.

NodeBLocalCell_maxNumEulUsers__Increase takes effect immediately. Decrease takes gradual effect; existing users are allowed to terminate normally until the new limit is reached. No new users are allowed until below limit.

NodeBLocalCell_maxNumHsPdschCodes__Increase takes effect immediately. Decrease takes effect gracefully (if more codes than the new limit are setup by RNC, the new limit will not apply until the RNC has reconfigured the physical shared channel so that less codes than the new limit are used).

NodeBLocalCell_maxNumHsdpaUsers__Increase takes effect immediately. Decrease takes gradual effect; existing users are allowed to terminate normally until the new limit is reached. No new users are allowed until below limit.
NodeBLocalCell_steeredHsCoreId__NodeBLocalCell::usageState is BUSY (the cell has been setup by the RNC).
NodeBLocalCell_uarfcnDl__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair1__At next unlock of local cell group.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair2__At next unlock of local cell group.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair3__At next unlock of local cell group.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair4__At next unlock of local cell group.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair5__At next unlock of local cell group.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair6__At next unlock of local cell group.
NodeBSectorCarrier_bandwidthDl__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBSectorCarrier_bandwidthUl__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBSectorCarrier_configuredMaxTxPower__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBSectorCarrier_eulThermalLevelPrior__At next setup of cell. If cell is setup and the noise floor is locked, at commit.. If cell is setup and the noise floor is unlocked, at next noise floor lock.
NodeBSectorCarrier_numOfRxAntennas__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBSectorCarrier_numOfTxAntennas__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBSectorCarrier_rfBranchRxRef__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBSectorCarrier_rfBranchTxRef__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBSectorCarrier_txBranchAPower__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
